(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 350.52 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 7abd00a8-233b-5aa3-b17d-f9051c2fd339))
(text "M.2 E-key directions are host TX->PET35/37 and PER41/43->host RX; Mu-side TX has 220n AC coupling." (at 20.32 358.14 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid efa9caeb-1b7f-5fd0-87b9-d327010667ad))
(text "USB2_P1 carries Bluetooth; default-BIOS HSIO3/REFCLK3/CLKREQ3 carry the E-key PCIe function." (at 20.32 365.76 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 53f2017c-4e83-5cad-8065-7c3ad150002f))
(text "Qualified radio is Intel AX210.NGWGIE.NV M.2 2230 Key-E: Wi-Fi over PCIe and Bluetooth over USB; AX211/CNVio2 is prohibited." (at 20.32 373.38 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 137c024a-f2eb-5c2b-acc8-789b32e6a2eb))
(text "OLED headers match common 4-pin SSD1306 modules: GND, VDD/3V3, SCK/SCL, SDA. Use 3.3V modules only." (at 20.32 381 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 1fdc29e1-d17c-52e4-9c58-b2b8242398ec))
(text "MAX-M10S V_BCKP, VCC, and VCC_IO use always-on MCU_3V3 so I/O cannot back-power an unpowered GNSS domain." (at 20.32 388.62 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 1fcacd03-3f0d-586d-b88c-6d7389d502c3))
(text "TCA9548A channels 0/1 isolate the identical 0x3C OLEDs; channels 2/3/4 isolate the three CH224A sinks." (at 20.32 396.24 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 87a9fe05-f4c5-5117-aa33-287967c5b556))
(text "Hardware-gated SERVICE_MUX_RESET_N asserts during every EC reset; firmware selects only a powered, VALID CH224A channel." (at 20.32 403.86 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 36462bad-3a0f-532e-a1a3-11128bcc89e4))
(text "GNSS RF layout: place U.FL near board edge, route RF_IN as 50 ohm, and keep it away from Wi-Fi antennas/noisy bucks." (at 20.32 411.48 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 56ffe551-ca61-5378-953f-6c8929d27a7b))
(text "U170 isolates powered-off E-key controls; R198/R199 keep WLAN and Bluetooth disabled until EC firmware explicitly enables them." (at 20.32 419.1 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid d93c3c2b-2fe9-5c3e-a4e1-45c22934e751))
(text "J42 is passive-antenna-only. Active antenna bias requires a complete u-blox short-protected supervisor, not a bias-tee strap." (at 20.32 426.72 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid e6e23825-48d6-54d7-9f9e-a02cd3e71569))
(text "SUSCLK, SDIO, PCM/I2S, UIM, and vendor-defined E-key pins remain NC for the AX210-class module target." (at 20.32 434.34 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c1115852-bb6b-5175-a87f-b3d44c61b12b))
(text "GNSS_EXTINT has no external pulldown; the MAX-M10S internal pull-up defines its reset state. EC firmware must leave the pin high-impedance until configured." (at 20.32 441.96 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 553558e7-2301-54cd-b880-58754f04b85e))
